<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Abank - Bank Card Types</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0-beta1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-0evSXBKJEiCTixQwlq2q77hbpQFz9CUfD2ygQvONKWuzK1q8uCxbCAmvTFCYbOgvBG" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        .card-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 10px;
        }

        .card {
            width: 30%;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .card-feature {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Abank - Bank Card Types</h1>
        <p>Choose the perfect card for your needs.</p>
        <div class="card-container">
            <div class="card">
                <h3 class="card-title">Зелена карта (Zelená karta)</h3>
                <ul class="card-features">
                    <li class="card-feature">Free card issuance</li>
                    <li class="card-feature">Up to 62 days grace period</li>
                    <li class="card-feature">Credit limit of 1000-200 000 UAH</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Order Now</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3 class="card-title">WOMЕТ</h3>
                <ul class="card-features">
                    <li class="card-feature">Credit limit of 1000-500 000 UAH</li>
                    <li class="card-feature">Up to 62 days grace period</li>
                    <li class="card-feature">Up to 20% cashback on selected categories</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Order Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0-beta1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-OgQ8iY4X0cuoiT+ch4fVEhDWLqZfu6c4FuFMO3xlUiU/yOoOOyp+zb/8mysH9xn" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>